profile:
Expert Electric - We're your neighborhood's electrician

We provide residential and commercial electrical services to: Vancouver, North and West Vancouver, Burnaby, New Westminster, Richmond, Delta, Coquitlam area, Maple Ridge, Pitt Meadows, Surrey, Langley, White Rock, Abbotsford and Mission.

We've got the power you need! Our trained electricians are the best in the industry, and can repair any issue, guaranteed! From installations to emergencies, big or small... our electricians can perform the job. We focus on the relationship and getting you the things you need to enjoy life!

Why call us first? 

•We are easy to reach - Real people answer our phones, not machines.
•1,000’s of parts on our trucks - For on the spot repairs in your home or business.
•Well Trained Courteous Technicians - we successfully perform repair to thousands of electrical problems every year.
•Up Front Guaranteed Pricing - you know the price before the work begins.
•24 hour emergency service.
•Quick response time
•Trained electricians
•Personalized scheduling

profile:
Master electricians are highly skilled electricians who generally work in a supervisory role or own contracting businesses. Many provinces require seven years of experience as an electrician or a bachelor's degree in electrical engineering for certification as a master electrician. Licensing specifics vary by province, but in numerous cases, a business with numerous journeyman electricians must have a master electrician who oversees the entire operation.

Thank you for taking the time in visiting my Ad. I am offering my 33 years of experience of end to end electrical services in any of these Electrical fields Industrial, Commercial, Agriculture and Residential. I specialize in Indoor/Outdoor Lighting, GFCI/Plugs, Exhaust/Ceiling Fans, Washer/Dryer, Microwave, Fridge, Relocating Electrical Devices, Air Conditioning, Hot Tub/Jacuzzi, Service Upgrades, Network Connections, Troubleshooting, Renovations to Equipment Repairs.... NO JOB TOO SMALL....I serve the entire Greater Vancouver, Lower Mainland and Fraser Valley. I also offer a one stop shop for all electrical needs. I have specialty knowledge in all things Electrical including Data Cabling, Security Systems and Facilities Management I am well regarded for the services I offer in these areas. Also strong knowledge of Designing, Estimating, Installing and Lines Specialists which is supported by a robust systems to ensure a job gets the focus and priority it deserves from start to finish you deserve to have an uninterrupted power supply and support for your electrical equipment.

I offer a FREE ESTIMATE in person but also I have been in the industry for over 33 years and for the most part can give an approximate quote over the phone as long as things are very well straight forward. I offer a great rate of $50 P/H with a MINIMUM 2 HOUR CALL OUT AT $100 OR A JOURNEY PERSON AND APPRENTICE $75 P/H MINIMUM  2 HOUR CAL LOUT $125 P/H.. EMERGENCY,WEEKEND AND AFTER HOUR RATES DOUBLE UNLESS AGREED BY BOTH PARTIES AHEAD OF TIME .... Please feel free to contact me to further discuss your needs and concerns at (778) 848-6122 Once again thank you for your time and I look forward to hearing from you as well as working with you.

I focus on serving my community and am actively involved and if you mention this Ad I will Donate 5% of my Labor Fee to your local Food Bank or Drug Prevention Program.   

I accept Visa, Mastercard, American Express, Cheque, Paypal, Email Transfer and Cash 
DO NOT contact me with unsolicited services or offers
